---
title: Saucy Roasted Veggie, Bacon & Pumpkin Ravioli with Baby Kale
description: Ravioli are like little gifts, pasta pockets packed with delicious pumpkin. Tie a bow around dinner tonight with a
tomato-based sauce with roasted capsicum, bacon and courgette for a perfect pasta present.
